# `.claude/` is local-only working state. The 3 canonical skill overrides
# (forge-code/plan/release) ARE tracked so CI link-check resolves the
# referenced `references/*.md` + `scripts/*.sh` files; everything else
# (worktrees, agents, state, etc.) stays local.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
.claude/skills/*
